data.description: Great home in an established country setting neighborhood free from HOA awaits your touch. This spacious 1.78 acre lot is beaming with plush grounds for a garden and lovely hardwoods. Inside, this 3 bedroom 2   bath home opens up to a lovely foyer and tray ceilings in the living room and master bedroom. The bright kitchen has a breakfast area and plenty of counter space to entertain guests. The HVAC and roof have been replaced since the original build and you will have room for your toys/tools in the 12x25 storage building. Only 11 miles from  Athens! Come check out this tucked away treasure! 24 hour notice for showing; see notes.  Seller is offering $10,000 allowance for upgrades, closing costs, rate buydown, and more with an acceptable offer.
